<shortdesc>Beginning with the Crypto Express6 adapter, when configured as a <keyword
conref="wskc_conref-l0wskc04.dita#conref-l0wskc04/cca"/> coprocessor, such a coprocessor is capable
of running in the <keyword conref="wskc_conref-l0wskc04.dita#conref-l0wskc04/pcihsm2016mode"/>. In
order for the requirements of <keyword conref="wskc_conref-l0wskc04.dita#conref-l0wskc04/pcihsm2016"
/> to apply to a workload, the workload must be using compliant-tagged key tokens.</shortdesc>
